body: Very rare for the cuck to win back in the end
One would think one of those doppelgänger would have taken out the other two and lived that kids life with those two sisters.
I gotta say having read none of the previous parts had me wondering what the fuck is happening.
Rip Shouji and especially Shouichi, you will both be remembered.  Especialy since Shouichi was the most unloved one out of the trio for 4 chapters.
I'll give the author credit, although I really disliked the story and found that it detracted from the art, it was at least original and it kept my attention.

This series REALLY needs a netorare tag. Shouma is repeatedly cucked by Shouichi and Shouji. In fact, he doesn't have any sexual contact with Ryou or Tomomi until the final chapter. Instead, he secretly masturbates - over and over again - while watching a pair of weird monsters fuck his sisters. The doppelgangers may *resemble* Shouma, and his desires do seem to have created Shouichi (while Ryou's desires apparently created Shouji). But that doesn't change anything. At least 90% of the story is pure netorare, and it only shifts to something more vanilla at the very end ... Overall, it's okay. I was initially intrigued by the dark fantasy element, but the art, characters and situations didn't do anything for me. And I wish the scans looked better. Pushing the contrast of low quality scans to get clean whites and pure blacks guarantees terrible results: destroys light lines and shading, crushes darker shading.
But yeah his sisters are almost a whore. I will just hope for the sister’s double yo appear and replace them
